      "side": 1,
      "message": "Michael, is my reasoning correct here? I think that if the inputOffset is 0,0, we\u0027re mostly correct? If I wanted to make things more correct (but not necessarily faster), I should be specifying inputBounds as the subset when I call asImage(), right? What\u0027s the easiest test to verify that works (vs. the current behavior)?",
